    public static enum Queryable.SelectOperator
extends java.lang.Enum<Queryable.SelectOperator>
    The operators that can be used with Queryable.select(String, SelectOperator, Object...).

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      BETWEEN
      Select rows where at least one value in the column is between the queries.
      CONTAINS
      Select rows where at least one value in the column is a substring of the query.
      EQUALS
      Select rows where at least one value in the column is equal to the query.
      GREATER_THAN
      Select rows where at least one value in the column is greater than the query.
      GREATER_THAN_OR_EQUALS
      Select rows where at least one value in the column is greater than or equal to the query.
      LESS_THAN
      Select rows where at least one value in the column is less than the query.
      LESS_THAN_OR_EQUALS
      Select rows where at least one value in the column is less than or equal to the query.
      NOT_EQUALS
      Select rows where no value in the column is equal to the query.
      NOT_REGEX
      Select rows where no value in the column matches the regex query.
      REGEX
      Select rows where at least one value in the column matches the regex query.
